<div class="grid_4 bot-1" id="sidebar">
    <h2 class="top-6 p2">Some Guidelines</h2>

    <p>I am happy to know the progress of SGM. Our student have done an excellent job in performing their role as member of society and carrying the mission of education. I wish SGM a grand success.</p>
    <p>Best of luck and warm wishes to Team SGM.</p>
    <p class="text-1 p3">       -Prof. S. G. Deshmukh<br/>(Director, ABV-IIITM)</p>

    <p>Expressing pleasure in words is not possible when I observe the success of Student Gyan Movement in a very short span of time.  </p>
    <p>Being a social creature, every human being on the earth must understand his/her responsibility towards the society in which he/she lives. Understanding this philosophy, our students take the responsibility of educating some children who are relatively far from a good education system. They started the Student Gyan Movement in the ABV-IIITM campus with the vision of best education without any monetary cost.  </p>
    <p>Of course, Education is not the only problem with the country, there are several others, e.g. Large Population, Corruption, Terrorism etc. But I feel that the lack of education is the root of all such problems. Other problems may significantly be controlled in a well educated and well cultured society.   </p>
    <p>Our students of ABV-IIITM Gwalior are doing a commendable job for the society. Simultaneously, children and their parents are equally responsible for the success of the movement.  </p>
    <p>I feel proud to my students who are involved in the movement. I congratulate to all children attending classes here, for their good start towards a better life. </p>
    <p>I feel very close to the fulfilment of the dream that SGM team has seen. My best wishes are always with SGM.  </p>
    <p class="text-1 top-2 p3">Dr. J. C. Bansal </p>
    <p class="text-1 top-2 p3">Dr. K. K. Pattanaik</p>
</div>
<div class="grid_8">
